https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354729%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESmarika%20plans%20to%20expand%20the%20area%20under%20vegetable%20cultivation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20received%20a%20great%20harvest%20of%20almost%2050%20tonnes%20per%20acre%20in%20the%20first%20year.%20We%20sold%20it%20in%20local%20%3Cem%3Emandis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(marts)%20and%20in%20other%20cities%20like%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20Patna%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20more.%20I%20have%20tied%20up%20with%20brokers%20with%20whom%20I%20pre-decide%20the%20rates%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20tomatoes%2C%20she%20also%20grows%20bottle%20gourd%2C%20cucumber%20and%20brinjal.%20The%20sowing%20and%20harvesting%20season%20is%20between%20May%20to%20March%2C%20with%20the%20cycle%20roughly%20around%20three%20months%2C%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20would%20only%20be%20able%20to%20harvest%20paddy%20twice%20a%20year%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20harvest%20vegetables%20many%20more%20times.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20much%20more%20profitable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%2C%20Dilip%20Rajan%20shared%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20a%20thousand%20square%20metres%20of%20land%20planted%20with%20bitter%20gourd%20will%20give%20a%20farmer%20roughly%20the%20same%20income%20as%20one%20hectare%20planted%20for%20rice.%20Vegetables%20can%20be%20harvested%20quickly%20(45-55%20days)%2C%20and%20three%20to%20four%20crops%20can%20be%20cultivated%20throughout%20the%20year%20to%20meet%20the%20increased%20demand%20for%20vegetables%20and%20changes%20in%20food%20consumption.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFarming%20is%20a%20viable%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20Smarika%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348771%2Fgrow-organic-food-doctor-naveen-kumar-farming-workshop-chennai-vegetables-fruits-at-home-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivating%20a%20variety%20of%20vegetables%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20her%20land.%20She%20now%20plans%20to%20add%2015%20acres%20more%20this%20year%20to%20her%20existing%2020.%20%E2%80%9CLast%20year%2C%20we%20received%20a%20harvest%20of%2055%20tonnes%20per%20acre%20for%20tomatoes.%20With%20this%2C%20our%20turnover%20was%20over%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20in%20FY%2023-24%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-11-1719572578.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tips%20to%20start%20vegetable%20farming%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-11-1719572578.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-11-1719572578-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-11-1719572578-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-11-1719572578-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-websit