get%20to%20hire%20a%20professional%20on%20a%20site%20like%20Fiverr%20or%20Upwork%20to%20manage%20our%20ad%20campaigns%2C%20we%20should.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20most%20things%20in%20life%2C%20there%20are%20no%20guarantees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20possibility%20that%20you%20put%20%24700%20in%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20week%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20get%20a%20single%20sale.%20That%20is%20a%20possibility%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20very%20quickly%2C%20you'll%20start%20to%20see%20data%20of%20how%20many%20people%20are%20seeing%20your%20ads%2C%20how%20many%20people%20are%20clicking%20in%20your%20ads%2C%20how%20many%20purchases%20you're%20getting%2C%20what%20the%20conversions%20are%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20you're%20working%20with%20a%20good%20professional%2C%20they%20can%20take%20that%20data%20and%20and%20tweak%20things%20and%20you%20should%20be%20able%20to%20get%20a%20pretty%20good%20idea%20of%3A%20Hey%2C%20if%20I%20put%20%24500%20into%20ads%20this%20month%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20get%20an%20extra%20%241%2C500%20in%20sales%20that%20I%20other%20otherwise%20wouldn't%20have%20got.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221172%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22peak%20pickleball%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68701018f748d8c055f5626b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221258%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20studio%20apartment%20doubles%20as%20the%20Peak%20Pickleball%20headquarters.%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b85c6ea-0688-4055-b135-c574b37f3493%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Think%20beyond%20Amazon%20and%20explore%20TikTok%20Shop%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20from%20Eugene%20Khayman%2C%20who%20built%20his%20own%20seven-figure%20Amazon%20business%20and%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-million-dollar-sellers-a-club-for-top-ecomm-entrepreneurs-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%