eople%20who%20know%20what%20they're%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20about%20putting%20yourself%20in%20a%20room%20with%20people%20that%20are%20smarter%20than%20you%2C%20so%20that%20you're%20growing%20faster%20and%20you're%20not%20making%20silly%20mistakes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMore%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20eCommerce%20Experiment%26quot%3B%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaunching-an-e-commerce-business-step-one-finding-business-partner-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EI%20started%20an%20e-commerce%20business%20with%20%245%2C000%20up%20front%20after%20writing%20about%20financially%20independent%20Amazon%20sellers.%20Here's%20how%20I%20doubled%20my%20budget.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilding-an-ecommerce-business-how-to-select-a-profitable-product-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMy%20friend%20and%20I%20pooled%20%2410%2C000%20to%20start%20an%20e-commerce%20company.%20After%20months%20of%20brainstorming%20products%2C%20we%20chose%20pickleball%20paddles.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-lanch-ecommerce-company-startup-costs-expenses-business-budget-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMonths%20into%20launching%20a%20pickleball%20eCommerce%20company%20with%20%2410%2C000%2C%20I'm%20already%20over%20budget.%20Here%20are%20all%20of%20my%20startup%20costs%2C%20including%20a%20surprise%20%242%2C095%20expense.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-mitigate-trump-tariffs-ecommerce-business-diversify-supply-chain-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMy%20e-commerce%20business%20sells%20pickleball%20paddles%20made%20in%20China.%20Tariffs%20haven't%20hit%20yet%2C%20but%20I'm%20r