igure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20closest%20Red%20Lobster%20is%20in%20Times%20Square.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20of%20the%20giant%20ad%20above%20the%20store%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BMaking%20the%20Impossible%2C%20Possible%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20felt%20comically%20inspirational%20in%20this%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20we%20%3Cem%3Ecan%3C%2Fem%3E%20eat%20an%20inordinate%20number%20of%20shrimp%20and%20crab%20legs!%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20walked%20in%20and%20were%20given%20a%20slip%20with%20a%20table%20number%20and%20instructed%20to%20go%20upstairs.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Red%20Lobster%20lobster%20tank%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68713d8d85e81483682dde6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20stopped%20by%20to%20say%20hello%20to%20our%20soon-to-be%20meal.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Jackson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20way%2C%20we%20passed%20the%20lobster%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20went%20around%203%20p.m.%20on%20a%20Thursday%2C%20and%20there%20was%20a%20decent%20showing%20for%20a%20relatively%20off-hours%20lunch.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Red%20Lobster%20dining%20room%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68713d3d3d5881a51c1d2f47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20was%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20diners%2C%20but%20it%20was%20relatively%20quiet.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Jackson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20expect%20Red%20Lobster's%20%245%20cocktails%20at%20this%20location%2C%20however.%20Times%20Square%20is%20one%20of%20the%20chain's%20few%20locations%20that%20doesn't%20offer%20happy%20hour%2C%20much%20to%20our%20surprise%20and%20disappointment.%20(We%20would've%20indulged%20for%20research%20purposes%20only%2C%20of%20course.)%20We%20went%20with%20a%20pair%20of%20strawberry%20lemonades%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAn%20insert%20in%20the%20menu%20prominently%20advertises%20Crabfest%20offerings%2C%20including%20the%20new%20seafood%20boils.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221204%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Red%20Lobster%20Crabfest%20menu%20showing%20seafood%20boils%2C%20steak%20or%20salmon%20Oscar%2C%20and%20the%20option%20to%20%26quot%3Bcrab-ify%26quot%3B%20your%20side%20dishes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687120a485e81483682dd893%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221438%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOther%20Crabfest%20offerings%20include%20steak%20or%20salmon%20Oscar%2C%20and%20crab-topped%20side%20dishes.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Jackson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECrabfest%2C%20a%20yearly%20event%20with%20limited-time%20crab%20offerings%2C%20started%20on%20June%2023%20and%20runs%20through%20September%2014%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20started%20our%20meal%20with%20the%20chain's%20famous%20Cheddar%20Bay%20Biscuits%2C%20of%20course.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Red%20Lobster%20Cheddar%20Bay%20biscuits%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687139db85e81483682ddda9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Cheddar%20Bay%20Biscuits%20were%20warm%2C%20salty%2C%20and%20slightly%20chewy.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Jackson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20(Sarah)%20told%20my%20friend%20we%20were%20going%20to%20Red%20Lobster%2C%20she%20was%20quick%20to%20remind%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20forget%20to%20try%20the%20%3Cem%3Ecrab%20bread%3C%2Fem%3E.%26quot%3B%20(Close%20enough%2C%20I%20guess.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cheddar%20Bay%20Biscuits%20were%20very%20warm%2C%20soft%2C%20and%20buttery%2C%20but%20could've%20had%20a%20stronger%20cheddar%20flavor.%20They%20were%20%3Cem%3Efine%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20I%20wasn't%20blown%20away%20by%20them.%20My%20editors%20and%20friends%20had%20all%20said%20beforehand%20that%20they%20were%20excited%20for%20me%20to%20try%20the%20iconic%20biscuits%2C%20so%20perhaps%20it%20was%20a%20tall%20order%20for%20anything%20to%20live%20up%20to%20that%20much%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFor%20the%20appetizer%2C%20we%20got%20the%20lobster%20dip.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Red%20Lobster%20Lobster%20Dip%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68713915f748d8c055f576df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20lobster%20dip%20had%20lumps%20of%20lobster%20and%20a%20cheesy%20topping.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20%2418.49%20and%20included%20Maine%20and%20langostino%20lobster%2C%20spinach%2C%20artichoke%2C%20and%20a%20three-cheese%20blend%20topped%20with%20pico%20de%20gallo%2C%20along%20with%20a%20side%20of%20tortilla%20chips.%20There%20was%20very%20little%20artichoke%2C%20and%20we%20could've%20done%20with%20a%20bit%20more%20spinach%20as%20well%2C%20but%20the%20dip%20had%20pretty%20sizable%20pieces%20of%20lobster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENow%20for%20the%20main%20attraction%3A%20the%20seafood%20boils.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Red%20Lobster%20seafood%20boils%20and%20cajun%20butter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68713bd385e81483682dde0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sailer's%20Boil%20came%20with%20two%20proteins%2C%20while%20the%20Mariner's%20Boil%20came%20with%20three.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Jackson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20one%20of%20each.%20For%20%2454.99%2C%20The%20Mariner's%20Boil%20includes%20a%20Maine%20lobster%20tail%2C%20a%20dozen%20shrimp%2C%20snow%20crab%20legs%2C%20corn%2C%20and%20red%20potatoes.%20The%20Sailor's%20Boil%2C%20priced%20at%20%2439.99%2C%20comes%20with%20two%20dozen%20shrimp%2C%20smoked%20sausage%2C%20corn%2C%20and%20red%20potatoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20added%20Old%20Bay%20and%20Parmesan%20flavors%20to%20the%20Mariner's%20Boil.%20The%20flavor%20additions%20weren't%20marked%20well%20on%20the%20menu%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20listed%20under%20an%20option%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BCrab%20Your%20Way%26quot%3B%20deal%2C%20which%20is%20different%20from%20the%20seafood%20boil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20customize%20for%20additional%20spice%3B%20we%20got%20the%20Sailor's%20Boil%20extra%20spicy%20with%20the%20roasted%20garlic%20butter%2C%20which%20our%20waiter%20said%20was%20the%20most%20popular%20flavor.%20Our%20waiter%20mentioned%20we%20could%20also%20get%20a%20flavor%20on%20the%20side%2C%20so%20we%20got%20the%20Cajun%20butter%20in%20a%20separate%20bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJordan's%20Mariner's%20Boil%20was%20appropriately%20spicy.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Red%20Lobster%20Mariner's%20seafood%20boil%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687138bc3d5881a51c1d2e4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Mariner's%20Boil%20costs%20%2454.99%20before%20tax.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrue%20to%20the%20added%20Old%20Bay%20and%20Parmesan%20flavor%2C%20I%20(Jordan)%20got%20the%20spice%20and%20herb%20taste%20I%20hoped%20for%20with%20a%20rich%20layer%20from%20the%20cheese.%20I%20made%20sure%20to%20dip%20each%20bite%20in%20the%20bottom%20of%20my%20bag%20to%20soak%20up%20as%20much%20sauce%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lobster%20tail%20that%20we%20shared%20was%20more%20than%20a%20little%20overcooked%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Sailor's%20Boil%20was%20a%20garlic%20lover's%20dream.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sailor's%20seafood%20boil%20from%20Red%20Lobster%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68713c17f748d8c055f57778%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20boil%20wasn't%20as%20spicy%20as%20we'd%20hoped%2C%20but%20very%20garlicky.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Jackson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20slight%20tingle%20on%20the%20tongue%20with%20this%20boil%20(remember%20that%20we%20ordered%20it%20extra%20spicy).%20But%20overall%2C%20it%20wasn't%20particularly%20hot%20to%20me%20(Sarah)%2C%20though%20I%20should%20note%20I'm%20a%20spice%20fiend%2C%20so%20very%20few%20foods%20ever%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sausage%20was%20incredibly%20salty%2C%20which%20felt%20like%20overkill%20when%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20boil%20and%20its%20seasonings%20were%20already%20heavily%20seasoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Red%20Lobster%20has%20stopped%20its%20%2420%20Endless%20Shrimp%20promotion%2C%20it%20felt%20alive%20and%20well%20with%20this%20boil%3B%20two%20dozen%20shrimp%20is%20no%20joke%2C%20and%20my%20stomach%20wasn't%20prepared%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20most%20struck%20me%20was%20how%20much%20minced%20garlic%20was%20in%20this%20boil.%20Garlic%20lovers%2C%20this%20is%20definitely%20the%20flavor%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Cajun%20butter%20was%20a%20little%20acidic%20for%20our%20taste.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Red%20Lobster%20Cajun%20butter%20flavor%20for%20seafood%20boil%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6871412285e81483682ddf0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20opted%20to%20try%20the%20Cajun%20butter%20on%20the%20side%2C%20so%20we%20could%20try%20all%20of%20the%20sauces.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Jackson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20sour%20and%20reminded%20Sarah%20of%20a%20vinaigrette.%20It%20tasted%20too%20much%20like%20lemon%20for%20Jordan's%20idea%20of%20a%20Cajun%20butter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20portions%20were%20more%20than%20we%20could%20eat%2C%20so%20we%20took%20leftovers%20to%20go.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221604%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Red%20Lobster%20Sailor's%20Boil%20seafood%20boil%20leftovers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68712dccf748d8c055f57479%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221210%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGarlic%20galore!%3Cp%3ESarah%20Jackson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20reference%2C%20this%20is%20how%20much%20of%20the%20Sailor's%20Boil%20Sarah%20had%20left%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20waiter%20kindly%20offered%20us%20a%20to-go%20container%20for%20our%20largely%20untouched%20side%20of%20Cajun%20butter.%20We%20politely%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20total%2C%20we%20spent%20%24145%20with%20gratuity%20included.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222545%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Red%20Lobster%20receipt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68715577f748d8c055f57bda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221909%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20grand%20total%20came%20out%20to%20%24145.78.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20subtotal%20for%20one%20appetizer%20and%20two%20seafood%20boils%20came%20out%20to%20about%20%24113.%20In%20true%20Times%20Square%20fashion%2C%20gratuity%20was%20included%20(thank%20you%2C%20tourism).%20Jordan%20concluded%20that%20it's%20an%20affordable%20price%20point%20for%20two%20seafood%20boils.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%2454.99%20Mariner's%20boil%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20a%20great%20deal.%20It%20allows%20you%20to%20get%20crab%2C%20shrimp%2C%20and%20lobster%20without%20paying%20as%20much%20as%20you%20would%20at%20many%20Cajun%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20for%20the%20road%2C%20we%20left%20with%20warm%20bags%20of%20Cheddar%20Bay%20Biscuits!%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cheddar%20Bay%20biscuits%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68713c9485e81483682dde3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20didn't%20expect%20to%20be%20given%20Cheddar%20Bay%20Biscuits%20to%20go.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Jackson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20our%20waiter%20brought%20us%20our%20to-go%20containers%2C%20he%20gave%20us%20some%20biscuits%20to%20take%20home%2C%20and%20I%20(Sarah)%20have%20to%20say%2C%20I%20liked%20these%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20the%20ones%20we%20ate%20in%20the%20restaurant%3B%20these%20ones%20seemed%20better%20flavored%20and%20seasoned%2C%20and%20also%20had%20a%20better%20texture.%20So%20it's%20possible%20it%20was%20just%20a%20%26quot%3Bbad%26quot%3B%20batch%20that%20disappointed%20me%20in-restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20who%20can%20say%20no%20to%20free%20bread%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-seafood-boil-review-photos-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752397381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68713aeb3d5881a51c1d2ec2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-seafood-boil-review-photos-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Red%20Lobster's%20new%20seafood%20boils%20are%20going%20viral%20on%20TikTok.%20We%20set%20out%20to%20see%20what%20all%20of%20the%20hype%20is%20about.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sjackson%40insider.com%20(Sarah%20Jackson%2CJordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-seafood-boil-review-photos-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Telang