n-d-rice-wheat-patent-wipo-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econventional%20crops%20like%20rice%20and%20wheat%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20are%20resilient%2C%20nutritious%2C%20and%20connected%20to%20our%20heritage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20understanding%20birthed%20a%20desire%20to%20bring%20these%20elements%20together%20in%20a%20thoughtful%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECooking%20with%20a%20conscience%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20left%20her%20full-time%20engineering%20job%20in%20early%202021%20to%20focus%20entirely%20on%20her%20research%20and%20vision.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20daunting%20to%20step%20away%20from%20the%20security%20of%20a%20steady%20career%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20I%20needed%20to%20dedicate%20myself%20fully%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20impactful%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20months%20went%20into%20experimentation%20and%20learning.%20The%20entrepreneur%20imagined%20a%20place%20where%20people%20could%20rediscover%20millets%20and%20traditional%20grains%20not%20as%20old-fashioned%20staples%20but%20as%20exciting%2C%20delicious%2C%20and%20sustainable%20food%20options.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20a%20space%20that%20would%20inspire%20people%20to%20rethink%20their%20choices%2C%20enjoy%20healthy%20food%20that%20tastes%20great%2C%20and%20understand%20the%20story%20behind%20every%20dish%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092807.982_11zon-1752206303.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20more%20than%202%2C000%20young%20students%20have%20attended%20the%20healthy%20eating%20workshop%20conducted%20by%20Nishtha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen