schools%20such%20as%20GEMS%20Genesis%20International%20School%2C%20Adani%20International%2C%20and%20Anand%20Niketan%2C%20it%20launched%20a%20series%20of%20immersive%20eco-workshops%20aimed%20at%20children%20aged%20five%20to%20eleven.%20Over%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20more%20than%202%2C000%20young%20students%20have%20taken%20part%20in%20what%20can%20only%20be%20described%20as%20a%20rewilding%20of%20their%20senses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20workshops%2C%20children%20arrive%20as%20they%20are%2C%20curious%2C%20giggly%2C%20often%20indifferent%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98healthy%20eating.%E2%80%99%20They%20begin%20by%20visiting%20the%20cafe%E2%80%99s%20own%20kitchen%20garden%2C%20where%20they%20are%20taught%20to%20touch%20the%20soil%2C%20identify%20native%20herbs%20like%20%3Cem%3Etulsi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(holy%20basil)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebrahmi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20harvest%20spinach%2C%20edible%20flowers%2C%20or%20carrots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20step%20into%20the%20kitchen%2C%20washing%20fresh%20vegetables%20and%20observing%20the%20staff%20as%20they%20chop%20and%20prepare%20the%20ingredients.%20Guided%20by%20the%20team%2C%20they%20assemble%20their%20own%20salads%20and%20millet-based%20snacks%2C%20gaining%20hands-on%20experience.%20They%20even%20get%20the%20chance%20to%20work%20with%20local%20fruits%20and%20herbs%2C%20using%20methods%20like%20cold-press%20juicing%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318779%2Fmillet-summer-drink-simple-easy-recipes-sorghum-bajra-ragi-shakes-smoothie%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20fresh%20drinks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20also%20take%20part%20in%20sound%20healing%20and%20aromatherapy%20sessions%20before%20sitting%20down%20to%20eat%20mindfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-med