-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T205157.563_11zon-1752247338-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T205157.563_11zon-1752247338-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468408%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20workshops%20cost%20Rs%2015%2C000%20per%20participant%2C%20covering%20all%20sessions%2C%20materials%2C%20site%20visits%2C%20and%20meals%20made%20from%20farm-fresh%20ingredients%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20factor%20that%20resonated%20most%20with%20her%20was%20how%20integrated%20the%20learning%20was.%20%E2%80%9CEverything%20we%20discussed%20in%20the%20theory%20sessions%20was%20already%20alive%20and%20implemented%20on%20the%20farm.%20It%20was%20not%20abstract%3B%20it%20was%20right%20there%20in%20front%20of%20us.%20The%20farm%20tour%20made%20everything%20click.%20We%20finally%20understood%20what%20it%20means%20to%20design%20with%20nature%2C%20not%20against%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20that%20clarity%20began%20to%20shift%20their%20everyday%20choices.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20stopped%20relying%20on%20delivery%20apps%20and%20began%20sourcing%20our%20food%20from%20local%20farmers%E2%80%99%20markets.%20We%20also%20replaced%20chemical-heavy%20products%20with%20natural%20alternatives%20and%20even%20started%20a%20small%20kitchen%20garden%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workshop%20gave%20them%20the%20confidence%20to%20think%20long-term.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20now%20seriously%20considering%20buying%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20where%20we%20can%20apply%20these%20principles.%20We%20have%20also%20started%20talking%20to%20friends%20and%20colleagues%20about%20sustainability%2C%20not%20by%20preaching%2C%20just%20by%20sharing%20what%20has%20changed%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3