ical%20frameworks%20to%20implement%20effective%20actions.%20It%20helps%20us%20understand%20and%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20local%20and%20global%20efforts%20on%20climate%20change%2C%20mitigating%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20and%20fostering%20skill%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20collaborations%20are%20fostering%20a%20new%20era%20where%20villages%20like%20Uda%20Majhlitand%20are%20not%20mere%20followers%2C%20but%20leaders%20steering%20environmental%20fortitude.%20Reflecting%20on%20the%20deeper%20meaning%20of%20the%20forest%2C%20Ghanshyam%20poetically%20remarks%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EJungle%20hi%20hamara%20jeevan%20hai%2C%20adivasi%20ke%20liye%20mahua%20unka%20ajeevika%20hai%20(%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20forest%20is%20our%20life%2C%20and%20through%20it%2C%20we%20thrive%20together).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752240786000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fjharkhand-mahua-1752234322.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D468032%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Uda%20Majhlitand%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Mahua%20was%20once%20a%20symbol%20of%20liquor%20and%20conflict.%20Today%2C%20it%20powers%20laddus%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20prosperity.%20The%20village%20embraced%20self-governance%20through%20Gram%20Sabhas%2C%20transforming%20livelihoods%2C%20reviving%20unity%2C%20and%20creating%20opportunities%20their%20children%20once%20only%20dreamed%20of.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F468032%2Fsamvad-climate-asia-transforms-jharkhand-village-bokaro-mahua-collection-self-governance-reliance%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mystery%20discovery%20in%20space%20is%20most%20likely%20the%20'oldest%20comet%20ever%20seen'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752240780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F07%2F1920x1080%