2%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epomegranates%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20try%20something%20unique%20and%20innovative%20%E2%80%94%20something%20no%20one%20else%20was%20doing%20in%20Beed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmeshwar%20tells%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20desire%20led%20him%20to%20explore%20the%20untapped%20potential%20of%20avocado%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvocado%2C%20a%20fruit%20celebrated%20for%20its%20nutritious%20value%2C%20was%20relatively%20unknown%20in%20the%20Marathwada%20region.%20Its%20growing%20demand%20stems%20from%20its%20benefits%20for%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F292447%2Ffruits-that-reduce-blood-pressure-diet-for-heart-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanaging%20blood%20pressure%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20diabetes%2C%20and%20heart%20health.%20%E2%80%9CI%20delved%20deep%20into%20research%20about%20the%20fruit%20and%20its%20advantages.%20I%20realised%20it%20could%20be%20a%20game-changer%20not%20just%20for%20my%20family%20but%20for%20the%20entire%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20avocado%20has%20come%20to%20symbolise%20Parmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20dedication%2C%20adaptability%2C%20and%20entrepreneurial%20spirit.%20A%20man%20of%20humble%20beginnings%20with%20ambitious%20dreams%2C%20his%20journey%20is%20a%20tale%20of%20perseverance%20and%20sustainable%20farming%20%E2%80%94%20demonstrating%20that%20even%20in%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20harshest%20agricultural%20environments%2C%20innovation%20can%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAvocado%20farming%20in%20challenging%20conditions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%2C%20who%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20of%20farmers%2C%20grew%20up%20immersed%20in%20the%20rhythms%20of%20rural%20life.%20Agriculture%20became%20his%20way%20of%20honouring%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20legacy.%20%E2%80%9CI%20always%20wanted%20to%20follow%20in%20my%20father